'''芽枝霉門'''（[[學名|學名]]：Blastocladiomycota）是[[真菌界|真菌界]]的一[[门_(生物)|門]]<ref name=Hibbett>{{cite journal | author=Hibbett, D.S., ''et al.'' | title=A higher level phylogenetic classification of the ''Fungi''| journal=Mycol. Res. | volume=111 | issue=5 | pages=509–547 | doi=10.1016/j.mycres.2007.03.004 | pmid=17572334|date=March 2007}}</ref>，生存於土壤及淡水之中，且絕大部份為[[腐生營養|腐生]]<ref name=margulis>{{Cite |title=Five kingdoms: an illustrated guide to the phyla of life on earth |authors=Lynn Margulis, Karlene V. Schwartz |publisher=Elsevier |year=1998 |isbn=0716730278 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9IWaqAOGyt4C&lpg=PT288&dq=Blastocladiomycota&client=firefox-a&pg=PT288#v=onepage&q=Blastocladiomycota&f=false |pages=216–217 |accessdate=2012-02-25 |archive-date=2014-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101090814/http://books.google.com/books?id=9IWaqAOGyt4C&lpg=PT288&dq=Blastocladiomycota&client=firefox-a&pg=PT288#v=onepage&q=Blastocladiomycota&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

芽枝霉門有一[[纲|纲]]、一[[目_(生物)|目]]、五[[科_(生物)|科]]。其中的三科中，有些物種為[[病原體|病原體]]，會感染[[水熊蟲|水熊蟲]]、[[水蚤|水蚤]]、[[線蟲|線蟲]]、多種水生和半水生的植物以及[[孑孓|孑孓]]等生物<ref name=margulis />。

芽枝霉門原本歸於[[壺菌門|壺菌門]]之中，但2006年對DNA序列的研究將其和其[[姐妹群|-{A]]——[[新美鞭菌門|新美鞭菌門]]提升為門<ref name=James>{{cite journal | author=James, T.Y., ''et al.'' | year=2006 | title=A molecular phylogeny of the flagellated fungi (''Chytridiomycota'') and description of a new phylum (''Blastocladiomycota'') | journal=Mycologia | volume=98 | pages=860–871 | url=http://www.mycologia.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/6/860 | doi=10.3852/mycologia.98.6.860 | pmid=17486963 | issue=6 | access-date=2012-02-25 | archive-date=2011-07-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727105619/http://www.mycologia.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/6/860 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

